data.title: About Us - People
data.meta_description: Who are we? We’re Xello! An education software company powered by passionate people committed to helping every student become future ready.
data.text:
When you were a kid, what career did you want to have?

When I was a kid I wanted to be an interior designer / professional organizer. I loved reorganizing and decluttering my parents home growing up and even to this day I will still secretly move things around in their home. Now having my own home, my favourite thing to do is shop for home decor and look at Pinterest boards of home design. I love decorating and the creative aspect of it.
